                        <title>Mobile-First Design Principles</title>
                </item>
                <item>
                        <description><![CDATA[<p>Learn how to create websites that look great on all devices, from mobile phones to desktop computers.</p><h2 id=mobile-first-approach>Mobile-First Approach</h2><p>Starting with mobile designs and scaling up ensures your site works well on all screen sizes.</p><h2 id=key-techniques>Key Techniques</h2><ul><li>Media queries</li><li>Flexible units (rem, em, %)</li><li>Flexible images</li></ul><h2 id=testing>Testing</h2><p>Always test on real devices when possible, not just browser dev tools.</p>]]></description>
